    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_6_2560-2620",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2560-2620",
      "markText": "在这些国家中，乡居的公民进城参加公民大会可以朝出暮归，人们相互间比较熟悉，一国政务比较简单，易于在公民大会中讨论和表决。",
      "totalCount": 2353,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2560&rangeEnd=2620",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2560&rangeEnd=2620"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_20_3089-3119",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "3089-3119",
      "markText": "共和国完了，继起的皇帝不要选民投票了，公民也成了驯顺的臣民。",
      "totalCount": 2349,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3089&rangeEnd=3119",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3089&rangeEnd=3119"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_10_17053-17102",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "17053-17102",
      "markText": "他的法律规定雅典公民分为富农、骑士、中农、贫民四级，全部有参加公民大会「Ecclesia」的权利。",
      "totalCount": 2345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=17053&rangeEnd=17102",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=17053&rangeEnd=17102"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_23_9679-9719",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "9679-9719",
      "markText": "不许一个政治集团把持政权，有别的政治集团和它对峙，谁上台，以取得选票的多少为准。",
      "totalCount": 2345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=9679&rangeEnd=9719",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=9679&rangeEnd=9719"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_11_8804-8853",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "8804-8853",
      "markText": "公元前480年开始的希波战争，希腊军是科林斯会议上成立的反波斯同盟的盟军，这个同盟的领袖是斯巴达。",
      "totalCount": 2329,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=8804&rangeEnd=8853",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=8804&rangeEnd=8853"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_18_9333-9392",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "9333-9392",
      "markText": "中国和西欧，在面临足以建立骑兵的新技术的时候，兵制一生产关系的反应之所以截然不同，是因为它们的政制和意识形态是不同的。",
      "totalCount": 2317,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9333&rangeEnd=9392",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9333&rangeEnd=9392"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_11_21367-21436",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "21367-21436",
      "markText": "伯里克理斯时代，相当部分的国库收入用于“装饰雅典”——修建建筑史上著名的雅典娜大庙、忒修斯大庙以及豪华富丽的、饰以巨大柱廊的雅典卫城正门。",
      "totalCount": 2313,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=21367&rangeEnd=21436",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=21367&rangeEnd=21436"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_20_8684-8720",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "8684-8720",
      "markText": "从这个意义上说来，正是较量中它没有占到便宜，才促使进步的批判发展了起来。",
      "totalCount": 2313,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8684&rangeEnd=8720",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8684&rangeEnd=8720"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_8_12539-12590",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "12539-12590",
      "markText": "“跨海迁移的第一个显著特点是不同种族体系的大混合，因为必须抛弃的第一个社会组织是原始社会里的血族关系。",
      "totalCount": 2306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12539&rangeEnd=12590",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12539&rangeEnd=12590"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_8_14270-14307",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "14270-14307",
      "markText": "这是因为他们在新地方建立新国家所能效法的楷模，还只能是他们所熟习的旧制度。",
      "totalCount": 2294,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14270&rangeEnd=14307",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14270&rangeEnd=14307"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_11_18814-18860",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "18814-18860",
      "markText": "现代史家计算，根据议事会成员不得连选连任的规定，雅典公民的1/3，一生中有机会被选入议事会。",
      "totalCount": 2286,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=18814&rangeEnd=18860",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=18814&rangeEnd=18860"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_10_14206-14254",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "14206-14254",
      "markText": "埃琉西斯、马拉松「Marathon」，或修尼阿姆「Sunium」的农民，已经认为自己是雅典人了。",
      "totalCount": 2274,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=14206&rangeEnd=14254",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=14206&rangeEnd=14254"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_18_885-946",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "885-946",
      "markText": "现在骑者可以稳稳地横矛于双臂与躯体之间来攻击打他的敌人，打击不仅来自他的肌肉，而且来自他本身和他疾驰前进的骑乘的联合重量。",
      "totalCount": 2274,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=885&rangeEnd=946",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=885&rangeEnd=946"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_9_16015-16128",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "16015-16128",
      "markText": "在此以前，福西斯各市邑之间本来就有部族性质的联合，战争中发展成为比较巩固的统一国家，按其性质而言，也可以称之为福西斯联盟，不过加盟的小市邑独立性不强，未必具有独立城邦的性质，所以福西斯国家，其实是自治的市邑联合组成的领土国家。",
      "totalCount": 2270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=16015&rangeEnd=16128",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=16015&rangeEnd=16128"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_11_11375-11417",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "11375-11417",
      "markText": "雅典帝国范围内纳贡的盟邦，每年交纳一定数额的贡款之后，它们的公民不再有服兵役的义务。",
      "totalCount": 2270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=11375&rangeEnd=11417",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=11375&rangeEnd=11417"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_11_17066-17111",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "17066-17111",
      "markText": "雅典公民，不仅在本国躬耕田间，还有机会躬耕于帝国范围内的海外地方，这就是“武装移民”制度。",
      "totalCount": 2270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=17066&rangeEnd=17111",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=17066&rangeEnd=17111"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "577837_11_19170-19277",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "19170-19277",
      "markText": "希波战争以后，雅典戏剧进入极其繁荣的时代，悲剧作家埃斯库罗斯、索福克勒斯「Sophocles」、幼里披底「Eur1pid」，喜剧作家阿里斯多芬「Aristophon」的著作，传遍整个希腊世界，为罗马时代作家所摹仿。",
      "totalCount": 2270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=577837&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=19170&rangeEnd=19277",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a323294058d12da32cf0843?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=19170&rangeEnd=19277"
    },
    {
